                     <hi rend="largeCaps">JOHN PHILLIPS</hi>
                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18391021-2791-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18391021-2791-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18391021-2791-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18391021-cd-92" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18391021-2791-offence-1 t18391021-cd-92"></join>10th of October</rs>, 20 skeins of silk, value 3<hi rend="italic">i</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. the goods of <persName id="t18391021-name-528" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-528" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-528" type="surname" value="SWAIN"></interp>
