                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-530" type="surname" value="GARRARD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-530" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT GARRARD</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 57.) I was called in and took the prisoner—I produce the silk.</p>
